{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──半年後。\n整体院は地域に根付いた整体院として営業していた。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "先生、こんにちは。今月もお世話になります。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "ナナちゃん、いらっしゃい。調子はどう？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "最近また肩こりがひどくて…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "やっぱり先生の施術が一番効くんです。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（まあ、これはこれで安定した関係かな…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "それは嬉しいな。今日も60分コースでいい？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "はい、お願いします。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "あの…例の特別なウェアも着た方がいいですか？",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "うん、あれを着ると効果が上がるからね。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "わかりました。最初は恥ずかしかったけど、今は慣れました…。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──施術中"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "ん…気持ちいいです…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "肩の凝りがだいぶほぐれてきたね。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "先生の手、本当に魔法みたいです。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（もっと攻めてもよかったかな…いや、これくらいが安全か…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──施術後"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "すごく楽になりました。ありがとうございます。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "それは良かった。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "先生、来月の予約も入れていいですか？",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "もちろん。第2火曜日でいいかな？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "はい、その日でお願いします。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_011"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "先生のおかげで、毎月調子が良くなります。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_012"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "君みたいな常連さんがいてくれて、本当に助かるよ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "そんな…私の方こそ、いつもお世話になってます。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_013"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──さらに数ヶ月後"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "先生、最近お店混んでますね。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_014"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "おかげさまでね。ナナちゃんみたいに定期的に来てくれる人が増えたんだ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "それは良かったです。先生の腕がいいからですよ。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_normal_015"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "ありがとう。そう言ってもらえると嬉しいよ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（これはこれで、いい関係なのかもしれないな…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "適度な距離を保ちながら、良い関係が続いていく。\nそれもまた、ひとつの幸せの形なのかもしれない。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "【NORMAL END - 良い顧客関係】",
      "triggerEnding": "normal"
    }
  ]
}